@database FTextClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - FText Class"


FText class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "TextClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The FText class is used to show a rasing frame text.

  Note that any attribute of Text class may be used with FText.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Inverse@{fg text}
  B ISGN
  Draws an inverted frame.

  @{fg shine}Shadow@{fg text}
  S IS
  MUI pen spec for the shadow pen.

  @{fg shine}Shine@{fg text}
  S IS
  MUI pen spec for the shine pen.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode
